author: @donnelly5757
text: Great video as always, but I will say this is a serious understatement.  Now that I'm out of work,  I am ever so glad that I have decided  to pursue this career path. Three great reasons to pursue data science: 1. Do something positive for society and gain a strong sense of purpose. 2. Something to keep the mind stimulated which can greatly help with depression and anxiety. 3. A solid career that can potentially help someone avoid being homeless and going down a dark path. I think these are solid enough reasons to purse this field.
